{"tid":1797622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動討論] 和你shop要唔要black bloc？","createTime":"2019-12-25T14:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:22:47.000Z","uid":336615,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a7826554eedf8860742638bc239db0ff0c61f19a","tid":1797622,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評：要black bloc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評：唔black bloc，街坊裝就得<br />\n<br />\n見隔離post開始檢討「和你shop」，大家可以嘗試拆開重要既行動決定來投票。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得無論街坊裝定black bloc，最重要係大家一齊做，咁先夠隱蔽。"},{"pid":"163aba2e3c37385c385342756ce123d96cdf765d","tid":1797622,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"建議唔裝修+唔black bloc"},{"pid":"65a94fd6c266b08e5d1d51ff7dc2e7ea2c690e8c","tid":1797622,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"163aba2e3c37385c385342756ce123d96cdf765d","tid":1797622,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"建議唔裝修+唔black bloc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"agree<br />\n<br />\npopo strategy<br />\n<br />\n1.啲便衣是但捉一件 然後附近啲人就會圍便衣救人 之後就可以名正言順話人襲警所以防暴入商場<br />\n<br />\n2. 忠誠勇毅嘅佢哋係唔怕經濟攬炒<br />\n怕經濟攬炒嘅只係施生陳生嗰啲收成期買晒鋪嘅人<br />\n呢個係上面嘅指令<br />\n佢地只會不斷咁樣irritate你<br />\n每隔一段時間就會irritate你<br />\n目的係想你哋開花，捉晒有膽量行動嘅人<br />\n剩返嗰啲今時今日都冇膽行出嚟嘅，將來23條呀國歌戲出咗之後更加唔會夠膽出聲，所以嗰啲人響上面來講係廢嘅，上面覺得只要捉實夠膽行出黎嘅就代表成功"},{"pid":"4aa6a2e0c1bb9b663d983ad143eceb35b4469fb2","tid":1797622,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"第一 不被捕<br />\n所以唔洗black bloc"},{"pid":"d255f37ef260d241cb3d90038cd6c13767c2627b","tid":1797622,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"帶多件黑色風褸無壞<br />\n換唔換就睇情況"},{"pid":"58f008c0042b2ab2770ed97c9872f4e7b0622dfa","tid":1797622,"uid":122571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"唔black bloc 靠人數塞爆個場"},{"pid":"51a12b243efc3b6a07b586646c3db58cb732ca4b","tid":1797622,"uid":169999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d255f37ef260d241cb3d90038cd6c13767c2627b","tid":1797622,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"帶多件黑色風褸無壞<br />\n換唔換就睇情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d37b54907502f1ac3146cfad9a86a4ce9b2cbf6a","tid":1797622,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d255f37ef260d241cb3d90038cd6c13767c2627b","tid":1797622,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"帶多件黑色風褸無壞<br />\n換唔換就睇情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"如果要black bloc，的確係要帶黑風䄛；如果預左唔black bloc，可能係多套非黑色衫換裝<br />\n<br />\n跟大隊會最好"},{"pid":"b33b0924a96a65f946ed69b196ac8927f1d6c8d7","tid":1797622,"uid":297112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163aba2e3c37385c385342756ce123d96cdf765d","tid":1797622,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"建議唔裝修+唔black bloc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"P仔無得比皮，推哩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce348432ecc6235304a649f59eeecaf8937cbdcf","tid":1797622,"uid":336615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"推呀，要多人投票先有參考價值"},{"pid":"c6066536d31e6470ed60d38bc6a3d3aa19cbc2d5","tid":1797622,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}